column5: Heading up to Minaki area on the 19th, was wondeing if anyone has any info. water levels, weather, fishing reports???

My dad has been up there for a while. I guess the water has dropped drasticaly in the last month and is actually a little low. That's hard for me to imagine as when I was there in late June it was higher than I have seen it in the last 20 years. He said the fishing wasn't the best......wonder why?
